  <brief_title>Effect of Multi-species Probiotic HOWARU® Restore, on Gut Microbiota of Elderly</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Multi-species Probiotic HOWARU® Restore, on Gut Microbiota of Elderly</official_title>
